author: Jenna Marie
text: Have you ever had someone love you while you wrestle through your past traumas? I did and he didn’t run, he didn’t argue, he didn’t manipulate, he didn’t blame,he listened and loved me. Find someone who will love you exactly as you are in every moment. I’m so thankful. I love you
